    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and is truly a rare find for a discerning buyer. The exterior is flawless, with original paint that retains a deep, showroom shine and no chips, scratches, or dents of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine, featuring premium materials that look and feel as they did the day it left the dealership, with no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history; it drives smoothly and reliably with all systems functioning exactly as intended. This is an exceptional example of the model, offering a like-new experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
