    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3. The S54 power plant remains naturally aspirated perfection, featuring crisp individual throttle bodies and seamless double VANOS engagement. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and fresh rod bearings for mechanical peace of mind. The 6-speed Getrag manual shifts with bolt-action precision, delivering power through a perfectly dialed-in limited-slip differential. Factory-spec dampening and pristine bushings ensure the chassis remains taut and communicative. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the discerning purist.",
